DESCRIPTION:Duke Innovation & Entrepreneurship invites you to seize the op
 portunity to see Duke student founders in action\, connect with groundbre
 aking Duke startups\, and unlock potential investment prospects. \n\n\nGe
 t inspired by exciting startups spanning diverse sectors like healthcare\
 , AI\, consumer goods\, services\, and energy. Cast your vote for the Bes
 t in Showcase venture\, and be there as more than $100K in non-dilutive p
 rizes are awarded at the final pitch session.  \n\n\nJoin us for an after
 noon where energy meets opportunity-and where your insights could help sh
 ape the landscape of tomorrow's business giants.
DURATION:PT3H
