CONTACT;X-BEDEWORK-UID=00f1fcdb-0f068baf-010f-068baf83-00000004:None
CREATED:20251125T213706Z
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy an afternoon of fresh creativity as graduating seniors f
 rom the Duke Department of Music share their latest work in the beloved a
 nnual Fountain Concert. Set in the airy lower atrium of the Biddle Music 
 Building-gathered around the central fountain-this informal event capture
 s the spontaneity\, camaraderie\, and joy of music-making at Duke.\n\nThi
 s concert will include performances by: Matthew Chen\, Abe Palmer\, Grace
  Peng\, Max Rong\, Elizabeth Sayler\, Marina Varriano\, and Eric Wang.\n\
 nA highlight of spring in the Music Department\, the Fountain Concert is 
 a celebration of student creativity and community-an invitation to pause\
 , gather\, and enjoy the sounds of Duke's emerging artists.\n\nFree and o
 pen to the public. All are welcome.
