DESCRIPTION:The first-year cohort of Duke's MFA in Dance warmly invites yo
 u to an evening of choreographic experiments and exchange. In an informal
  and open setting\, we will share fresh work developed over the course of
  the term. These inquiries into movement\, relation\, and perception invi
 te both reflection and encounter\, as we test\, expand\, and give form to
  emerging ideas. Join us for an hour of curiosity\, inspiration\, dialogu
 e\, and shared attention. We look forward to welcoming you to the Ark. Re
 freshment provided.
DURATION:PT1H
